{"tid":771994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩街坊Look視察工廠 笑到見牙唔見眼","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T02:51:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":217,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"8790129ebdec4a397cf4e27a956745add7e44d26","tid":771994,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"(新增動新聞)<br />\n北韓官媒周三報道領袖金正恩與夫人李雪主一同視察海鮮醬廠等工廠，了解生產情況，他未有穿上常見的中山裝示人，反而頭戴草帽配寬鬆白上衣及西裝褲，一身「街坊Look」出場，認真親民貼地。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩與李雪主視察金山浦海鮮醬加工廠，期間他要求工人聆聽人民所需，改善海鮮醬味道，以及增加海鮮醬品種，為人民的飲食生活做實際貢獻。未知是否當地天氣熱，金正恩才以一身輕鬆裝扮示人，不過李雪主以及其他高官仍穿著整齊陪伴視察。<br />\n報道未有提及金正恩視察工廠的確實時間，不過今次並非他首次到訪這間海鮮醬加工廠，工廠由軍方管理，2015年3月仍在興建時，金正恩已來到地盤視察，他去年1月在工廠落成後又再次到訪。<br />\n金正恩自6月底起不斷到全國各工廠視察，相信他最近身處黃海南道。<br />\n韓聯社  <br />\n<br />\n金正恩視察工廠開懷地笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180808/small/1533716347_c50c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180808%2Fsmall%2F1533716347_c50c.jpg&h=8c395677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正恩以「街坊Look」示人<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180808/small/1533707547_a3da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180808%2Fsmall%2F1533707547_a3da.jpg&h=bfe406d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正恩與李雪主一同視察海鮮醬廠<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180808/small/1533708013_948b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180808%2Fsmall%2F1533708013_948b.jpg&h=7cdb4905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180808/58536678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58536678&d=y8y8TxoB%2BWH7vemxOF3vhcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2f9872bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk